Jenna Thomas was strangled to death by Philip Packer in 2008 . 
  Her sister Nikki Thomas says she wishes she had done more to stop her ex-boyfriend from stalking her . 
  He bombarded her with hundreds of calls and texts a day but she never reported him to police . 
  Nikki appeared on This Morning to tell how her sister was murdered by her ex . 
  She is warning others not to tolerate stalking behaviour . 
 